# Ad-hoc visual-verification screenshots written by playwright MCP /
# manual checks. Local only; never committed. Anchored to repo root
# so subdir paths like `docs/screenshots/` (the committed README
# captures) and `docs/fixtures/screenshots/` aren't caught.
/screenshots/

